## 3. Verification & Testing Plan

### Automated Tests
*   Run unit tests on the **Content Editor** to verify blacklisted word detection and title length constraints.
*   Run mock database tests validating that duplicate titles are rejected.
*   Run API test calls to `wix-mcp` using a sandbox site to verify collection reads/writes.

### Manual Verification
*   Deploy the engine locally and run an end-to-end dry run.
*   Inspect the Wix CMS dashboard to confirm that the generated collection items (projects) are populated correctly with the corresponding fields and categories.
